  "title": "O&G Staff Nurse (Office hours) #HJO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide nursing support in O&G clinics settings</li><li>Assist doctors and registered nurses during consultations, procedures</li><li>Monitor and record patients’ vital signs, conditions, and progress.</li><li>Administer treatments under supervision.</li><li>Provide patient education and emotional support for patients and families.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in O&G / maternity ward / women’s health nursing is an advantage.</li><li>Compassionate, patient-focused, and able to work in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Strong teamwork and communication skills.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p><p><br /></p><p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
